Online alternative:

	react.new (in browser)


Setup: Create React App (webpack)

    Create Project

        $ npx create-react-app <project-name>

    Project info

        public/index.html has a div with id=root


        scr/index.js has react code

            import React from "react";
            import ReactDOM from "react-dom/client";
            import "./index.css";

            function App() {}

            const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root"));
            root.render()

    Start Project

        $ npm start

    Edit project

        src/index.js

Setup: import React App (webpack)

    open the folder in vscode and open a terminal

    $ npm install